Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:59.73,default,,0,0,0,,A ship, on which desperate folk\Ngather for a night of gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き詰まった者たちを集めての
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一夜限りのギャンブル船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.41,default,,0,0,0,,the ship of hope, Espoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の船 エスポワール
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.70,default,,0,0,0,,The gamble which Kaiji and the\Nrest will be taking part in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちに提供された
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:08.79,default,,0,0,0,,...consists of four cards each\Nof Rock, Scissors and Paper:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グー チョキ パー 各４枚ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:11.03,default,,0,0,0,,a game of\N12 cards in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,計12枚のカードを使った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's Restricted Rock,\NScissors and Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:20.36,default,,0,0,0,,Now, please open envelope B\Nwhich you were handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:18.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では皆様に手渡した このＢの袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらを開封してください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:26.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 星？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.58,default,,0,0,0,,Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.75,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Open Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:28.86,default,,0,0,0,,You should find three stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このような星が３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てきたはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.87,default,,0,0,0,,They are meant to be attached\Nto the plate on your left pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆様の左胸のプレートに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,付けられるようになってます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:38.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３つの星を付けてください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.11,default,,0,0,0,,Please put them on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:42.11,default,,0,0,0,,That's all,\Npreparations are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以上です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで準備は すべて終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要するにカードでジャンケンをし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.19,default,,0,0,0,,Use the cards to play\NRock, Scissors and Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸の星を奪い合っていただく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.49,default,,0,0,0,,...and get your opponents' stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.85,default,,0,0,0,,That's what the game is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ それだけのゲームです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホールマスター利根川の説明は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:52.77,default,,0,0,0,,Hall master Tonegawa\Nthen proceeded to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケンのルールへと移る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.56,default,,0,0,0,,...the rules of Restricted\NRock, Scissors and Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに戦う意志を確認したら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢チェック｣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.43,default,,0,0,0,,To start a duel, say "Check".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.40,default,,0,0,0,,Then say "Set".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いて｢セット｣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に｢オープン｣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.76,default,,0,0,0,,Finally, say "Open".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけである
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこなら星の移動はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.44,default,,0,0,0,,The stars don't change hands\Nif it's a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし勝負があったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:12.67,default,,0,0,0,,But upon a win, the winner\Ntakes one star from the loser,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝者は敗者の星を１つ受け取り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の胸に付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:14.91,default,,0,0,0,,and attaches it to his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これをここにいる全員で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由に相手を決め 繰り返すだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.26,default,,0,0,0,,Choose your opponents freely\Namong those present here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.68,default,,0,0,0,,and repeat the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.92,default,,0,0,0,,The used cards will be\Nplaced inside a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使用したカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボックスの投入口に入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.60,default,,0,0,0,,The cards in the box will be\Nindicated by the electric board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボックスに入れられたカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電光掲示板に表示される
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,配られたグー チョキ パーの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードは それぞれ４枚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:33.05,default,,0,0,0,,Each participant was given\Nfour of each type of card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,参加者は103名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:38.02,default,,0,0,0,,There are 103 participants in all,\Nhence 412 of each card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部で412枚ということになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.43,default,,0,0,0,,The duration of the game\Nis four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の時間は４時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負 途中の経過はどうあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.63,default,,0,0,0,,You win if you manage\Nto keep your three stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終的に星を３つ確保すれば勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.64,default,,0,0,0,,no matter the results\Nduring the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.44,default,,0,0,0,,It's simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純にして明快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし12枚のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて使い切ること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.59,default,,0,0,0,,But you must use up\Nall 12 of your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを破棄することは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.31,default,,0,0,0,,Disposal of the cards\Nare not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーム終了時に星が２つ以下の者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.19,default,,0,0,0,,When the game is over,\Nthose with two stars or less,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星が３つ以上あっても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,those with three stars or more\Nbut failed to use up their cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間内にカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使い切れなかった者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードがあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,途中で星をすべてなくした者は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:09.43,default,,0,0,0,,and those who lost all their\Nstars are considered losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けである
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.38,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nin this gamble,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うならば 今回のギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は寿命　カードはチャンス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.96,default,,0,0,0,,the stars are your life gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.17,default,,0,0,0,,And the cards\Nare your chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗者が残したカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,主催者側の手でボックスに投入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:21.48,default,,0,0,0,,The organisers will put the\Nleftover cards into a box,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:25.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの残数に違いは生じない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:24.18,default,,0,0,0,,to make sure there is no mistake\Nin the total number of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.68,default,,0,0,0,,No mistake in the\Ntotal number of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.38,default,,0,0,0,,That's the end\Nof my explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以上で私の説明は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて終わらせていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆様の健闘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.59,default,,0,0,0,,I wish all of you\Na good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心からお祈りしております
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと この借りた金は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.15,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.66,default,,0,0,0,,What do we do with\Nthe money we borrowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ ご自由に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.40,default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.63,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に申し上げましたとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:50.63,default,,0,0,0,,I said at the start that we\Nwill not answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,質問は一切 受け付けません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍資金の件は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:55.37,default,,0,0,0,,Please use your war funds\Nas you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各自 ご自由に判断し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お使いください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由にって…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けた時はどうなるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.08,default,,0,0,0,,As we see fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:58.98,default,,0,0,0,,What happens when we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時の処遇について話してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.88,default,,0,0,0,,Tell us\Nwhat will happen then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は仲介のヤクザから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船で聞けって言われたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.38,default,,0,0,0,,The yakuza middlemen told me\Nto ask onboard the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:09.82,default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, but we are unable\Nto answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:11.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,質問には一切 お答えできません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:11.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたら どうなるかぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話すのが当然だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.18,default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you at least tell us\Nwhat happens if we lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　ふざけんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.26,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Don't mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.32,default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカにしやがんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.26,default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, yeah!\N- Are you insulting us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.96,default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶち殺すぞ　ゴミめら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.50,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!\NYou lot of trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.51,default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らの質問に答えるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.51,default,,0,0,0,,It is easy to\Nanswer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:38.51,default,,0,0,0,,But what's the point of asking\Nwhat will happen when you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:39.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ここで負けた時の処遇を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:39.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いて どうなる？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな話を聞きたいのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらでもしてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.52,default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to hear,\NI can tell you all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ここにいるお前らに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:48.41,default,,0,0,0,,But you have no way\Nof confirming the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その話の真偽を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かめるすべはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも聞きたいと言うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.93,default,,0,0,0,,Do you still want to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らはシャバでの戦いに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けに負け 今 ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:56.93,default,,0,0,0,,All of you are here because\Nyou're losers in society itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰からも愛されることなく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:01.07,default,,0,0,0,,You're all loved\Nby no one, broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貧窮し ウジウジと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:05.67,default,,0,0,0,,...and crawling around\Nthe fringes of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人生の底辺を這って這って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,這い回ってるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.94,default,,0,0,0,,Rather than think of what hell\Nyou'll face after losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けて行き着く先が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄うんぬんより
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ここがすでに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄の釜の底だということが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.54,default,,0,0,0,,why can't you realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:16.18,default,,0,0,0,,...that you're already at\Nthe pit of hell's cauldron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ分からんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 糸は垂れている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.69,default,,0,0,0,,But you're still\Nhanging by a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,およそ半数は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この釜の底から引き上げられる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.96,default,,0,0,0,,About half of you will be\Npulled out of this cauldron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.70,default,,0,0,0,,What you should be\Ndoing now is to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが今 成すべきことは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って ここから抜け出ること
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.70,default,,0,0,0,,Win, and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心に刻め　勝つこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.06,default,,0,0,0,,Grind it into your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.90,default,,0,0,0,,To win...\NWinning is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つことだけがすべてだと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければゴミ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.53,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't win, you're trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:44.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければ！勝たなければ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.31,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.18,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.94,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.95,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa stepped down\Nafter that resounding speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は げきを飛ばし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壇上から降りた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.26,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負が始められた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.35,default,,0,0,0,,The game began!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ… どうすりゃいいってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:15.04,default,,0,0,0,,At a glance, there's a\N50-50 chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一見 この勝負 生き残る可能性は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,五分五分に見える
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし何かあるはずだ　何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:21.73,default,,0,0,0,,But there must be something to\Nincrease the odds of victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ確率を高める何か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.30,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ　やったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初の敗北者が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.05,default,,0,0,0,,The first loser has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:34.29,default,,0,0,0,,In under 10 minutes of the game,\Nhe lost all his three stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負が開始されて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分もたたぬうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:36.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 星を３つ失ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:41.03,default,,0,0,0,,In this gamble, each round is\Nplayed in less than 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１戦するのに10秒とかからない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１度も勝てずに３連敗すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗北決定まで数分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:46.04,default,,0,0,0,,Losing three in a row\Ntakes just a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるとなったら早い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.64,default,,0,0,0,,One can be out of\Nthe game very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.78,default,,0,0,0,,One by one, the losers appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続々 敗者が決定する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 考えてんだ こいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,What are these guys thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.63,default,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to have\Nlost a major challenge at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても大勝負に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたって顔じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんさんの思ってること分かるで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.82,default,,0,0,0,,I know what\Nyou're thinking, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負 負けたら廃人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.84,default,,0,0,0,,If you lose this game,\Nyou're as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死をも覚悟して
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臨むべきギャンブルや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.63,default,,0,0,0,,It's a gamble one should face\Nwhile resolved to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運否天賦で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるようなもんやない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.74,default,,0,0,0,,It's not something to\Nbe left to pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で俺の名前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.59,default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.84,default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.20,default,,0,0,0,,During the lending of funds,\Nyou were behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 貸し付けの時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の後で限界まで借りとった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.24,default,,0,0,0,,...and borrowed to\Nthe maximum limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,印象深かったんや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人は できる人や思うてな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:25.64,default,,0,0,0,,That left an impression on me\Nthat you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたかて ひょっとして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の名前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.91,default,,0,0,0,,Do you... remember\Nwhat my name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.15,default,,0,0,0,,Funai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.15,default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I'm so glad\Nyou remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うれしいで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えとってくれたんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.16,default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\NYou're acting too familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせよ　なれなれしいぞ てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:44.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言わんと カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.94,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mr. Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,組もうやんか 俺とあんた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.41,default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we team up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え 組む？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.02,default,,0,0,0,,- Team up?\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このギャンブル 生き残るには
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パートナーが必要なんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.30,default,,0,0,0,,To survive this gamble,\Na partner is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きちんとしたパートナーさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つかれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.54,default,,0,0,0,,If you can find\Na good partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100％ 勝ち残れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.54,default,,0,0,0,,you have a 100% chance\Nof winning till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.24,default,,0,0,0,,100%?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100％？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.18,default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.06,default,,0,0,0,,Quit fooling around!\NThere's no such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと あるわけねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:11.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　この勝負 勝つには
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:11.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どないしたら いいんやった？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.89,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiji, what were we\Ntold to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.29,default,,0,0,0,,...in order to win this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.13,default,,0,0,0,,Finish using all the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カード全部 使い切って…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:17.51,default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.12,default,,0,0,0,,Three stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.16,default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:25.63,default,,0,0,0,,Having three stars mean to\Nmaintain your current status.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その星３つっちゅうとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現状維持でいいってとこがミソや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.83,default,,0,0,0,,Anyone will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰でもいい　誰かと組んで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出来レースをするんや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.87,default,,0,0,0,,Team up with someone and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,12回連続の あいこにしたらええ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.20,default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで条件は満たす
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.11,default,,0,0,0,,That would fulfill\Nall the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードをすべて使い切り 星３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:40.85,default,,0,0,0,,We use up all the cards\Nand each keep three stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.15,default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:45.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.20,default,,0,0,0,,100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100％や
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.72,default,,0,0,0,,It's a 100% way of survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで100％ 生き残れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.17,default,,0,0,0,,You figured all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 よくそんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.97,default,,0,0,0,,I am a repeater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はリピーターなんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リピーター？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.30,default,,0,0,0,,Repeater?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:08.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 俺以外にも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:08.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちらほら見かけんで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.44,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:11.27,default,,0,0,0,,I see some familiar faces here\Nfrom the previous ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前回の船で顔を合わせた連中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.05,default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!\NIsn't that unfair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不公平じゃねえか そんなの！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:19.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ… 今そのことで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:19.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹を立てとる場合とちゃうって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.90,default,,0,0,0,,Well, now's not the time\Nto be angry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実はな カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:24.29,default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mr. Kaiji,\Nyou can sell these stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この星 売れるんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.03,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 売れる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の終了と同時に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:31.00,default,,0,0,0,,When the game ends, those with\Nextra stars start selling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:33.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星足らずの者に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:33.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余った星の売買が始まるんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.27,default,,0,0,0,,At a rate of a few million\Nfor one star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:37.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ何百万って値でな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.00,default,,0,0,0,,This money is for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は その時に使われるんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.70,default,,0,0,0,,But in that case, even if\Neveryone tries to draw,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.06,default,,0,0,0,,someone will betray\Ntheir partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:44.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:44.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこにしようと思っても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.95,default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of\Ngetting more stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この星 欲しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏切るもんが必ず現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし このギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.80,default,,0,0,0,,Although there's a perfect way\Nto survive this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りの必勝法はあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:56.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を増やす必勝法はない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:56.70,default,,0,0,0,,there is no sure way\Nto increase your stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まともに戦えば半数は死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:01.29,default,,0,0,0,,If we fight it out squarely,\Nhalf of us will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:05.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたら しまいや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.92,default,,0,0,0,,If we lose, it's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:10.46,default,,0,0,0,,Rumour has it that some are\Nlocked up to do forced labour,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:10.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,噂じゃ 監禁されて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:10.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強制労働させられるちゅう話とか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.20,default,,0,0,0,,and others, after being\Nused as guinea pigs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:16.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開発中の新薬の実験台にされ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:16.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廃人になったちゅう話もある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.49,default,,0,0,0,,...for drug experiments,\Nbecome paralysed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええか カイジさん　この船は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一にも負けられへん船なんや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.39,default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mr. Kaiji. We can't afford\Nto lose on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲かいたらあかん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き分けで生き残るんや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:25.10,default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't be greedy.\NSurvive by drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで借金はチャラ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:29.42,default,,0,0,0,,And with the debt cleared,\Nisn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:31.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで十分やないの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:31.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.05,default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に生き残ろうや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.22,default,,0,0,0,,Let's survive this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.34,default,,0,0,0,,I want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ そうしたいけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.03,default,,0,0,0,,I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと問題が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.54,default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 1000万借りたから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.40,default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll have an interest\Nof 4 million at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の終わりに400万以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金利が付く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:51.94,default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I need\N3.85 million to clear my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは 俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャラにしてもらう借金は385万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから アシが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.34,default,,0,0,0,,So, my funds are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かーっ　カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.85,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Kaiji,\Nyou don't understand at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた　全然 分かってへんな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき金貸す時 10分複利って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うとったやないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.11,default,,0,0,0,,Didn't they say the interest\Naccumulates every 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:03.92,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分複利ってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:09.56,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it adds up\Nevery 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分刻みで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金利が付くっちゅうこっちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり さっさと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負 終わらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.20,default,,0,0,0,,Which also means that if\Nyou finish the duel quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.16,default,,0,0,0,,you'll have less interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,超安い金利ですむんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今やったら 20分以内で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わらすことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:18.13,default,,0,0,0,,If we start now,\Nwe can finish in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゅうことは 30万ちょいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金利ですむっちゅうこった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:23.05,default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll end up with\Nan interest of 300,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30万？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうや　だから言うとるやないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.87,default,,0,0,0,,300,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.38,default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:29.09,default,,0,0,0,,And that's why they say\Ntime equals to money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時は金なり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は１分かて惜しい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.88,default,,0,0,0,,Even one minute\Nis too much to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.99,default,,0,0,0,,With that,\NKaiji accepted the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしてカイジは誘いに乗る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.85,default,,0,0,0,,And started to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.39,default,,0,0,0,,You got it? Don't mix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええか　間違えるんやないで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出す順番はグー チョキ パー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.63,default,,0,0,0,,The sequence is\NRock, Scissors, Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.36,default,,0,0,0,,If we play quickly,\Nit won't even take two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:48.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,テキパキやったら２分もかからん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほな 行くで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.06,default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？あ… ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.60,default,,0,0,0,,- Check.\N- Huh? R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット　オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.10,default,,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.34,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.81,default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悪魔じみた船で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天は俺を見捨てなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:08.18,default,,0,0,0,,Heaven has not abandoned me\Non this devil-forsaken ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井さんのような人に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巡り合わせてくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.54,default,,0,0,0,,It arranged for me to\Nmeet someone like Funai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.38,default,,0,0,0,,I am indeed fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.52,default,,0,0,0,,They continued to draw\Nfor nine rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:18.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９回連続あいこ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.98,default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Kaiji and Funai\Nwill finish their cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:22.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでカイジも船井も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:22.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順調にカードを消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異変は10回戦目に起こる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.33,default,,0,0,0,,But something happened\Nin the 10th round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.27,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.00,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:31.94,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちゃー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.64,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!\NWhat have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何ちゅうミスを！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勘違いしてもうた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.36,default,,0,0,0,,I made a terrible mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すんまへん カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すんまへん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.11,default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, Mr. Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.75,default,,0,0,0,,No choice then!\NLet's equal up at the next go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃあない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次で帳尻合わせましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次 これで勝負するさかい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.75,default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.27,default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:52.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井は これから出す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:52.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーのカードをひらつかせながら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:51.76,default,,0,0,0,,Funai showed Kaiji\Na Rock card,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:56.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒服の手前 形の上だけだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:56.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を１つ 持っていった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:55.29,default,,0,0,0,,...and took a star from him\N"just for show",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.96,default,,0,0,0,,since they were\Nbefore a man in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.40,default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.70,default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:05.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:05.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せめてこの時 気づいていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.57,default,,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.02,default,,0,0,0,,If he noticed at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.74,default,,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:28.33,default,,0,0,0,,When I knew I was coming\Nonboard, I practised hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船に乗ることが決まってから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざん練習してきたんや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:32.93,default,,0,0,0,,How to place two cards\Nback-to-back perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードをピタッと２枚 重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手に見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,置いてくるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せてない裏側のカード
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:37.00,default,,0,0,0,,displaying one side to the\Nopponent and using the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事な手際やったやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.94,default,,0,0,0,,I was clever, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.64,default,,0,0,0,,Right! See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:46.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほな 俺はこれで ごちそうさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.18,default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… 待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.18,default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.34,default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.62,default,,0,0,0,,Are you still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 寝ぼけとるんや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うたろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.68,default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星１つが何百万って値で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売れるんや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.69,default,,0,0,0,,The stars are worth\Na few million each.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はよう この船の本質を理解して
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.88,default,,0,0,0,,Unless you grasp the situation\Nquickly and move accordingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.12,default,,0,0,0,,you will go through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなりの動きせんと地獄見るで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.68,default,,0,0,0,,But it might already\Nbe too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう手遅れかもしれへんけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.42,default,,0,0,0,,Funai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負開始後 わずか20分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.20,default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes\Nafter the game began,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは命同様の星を２つ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:20.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji was cheated of two stars\Nthat were worth his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わけの分からぬうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だまし取られた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.65,default,,0,0,0,,Funai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:33.79,default,,0,0,0,,FUNAI! You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:34.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井　ふざけるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返せ！俺の… 俺の星 返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何や　何するんや　放せ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.85,default,,0,0,0,,Give them back!\NMy... My stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:37.85,kaiji-overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.10,default,,0,0,0,,- Give them back!\N- Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら 何してる お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.23,default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.16,default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.77,default,,0,0,0,,- Get back.\N- Funai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離れろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け　何だ 一体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.50,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:54.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,This scum, he...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:59.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいこの約束を裏切って…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:59.92,default,,0,0,0,,He went back on his word\Nabout drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あほんだら！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 俺の何や？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.25,default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.45,default,,0,0,0,,What are you to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものの５分も話さんかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.76,default,,0,0,0,,You thought we were friends\Nafter a five-minute chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達にでもなったつもりか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,甘ったれが！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.76,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は おんどれを取って食うた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ それだけや
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.45,default,,0,0,0,,I have just preyed\Nand fed on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.76,default,,0,0,0,,That's all, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソが　騒ぐな ゴミ虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.70,default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a scene,\Ntrash maggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.76,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:18.75,default,,0,0,0,,Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上もめると お前は退場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も散れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.55,default,,0,0,0,,If you keep acting like this,\Nyou'll be ejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.77,default,,0,0,0,,You too. Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴の言うとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も問題はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:29.29,default,,0,0,0,,Like he said,\Nthere's no problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.98,default,,0,0,0,,This is where you guys bet\Nthe remainder of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが後の人生を賭けて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦っている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うならば戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.45,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, a warzone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その戦場で後ろから撃たれたと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騒ぎ立てる兵士が どこにいる？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.39,default,,0,0,0,,Which soldier\Nmakes a fuss and cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.42,default,,0,0,0,,...after getting shot\Nfrom behind in a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は今 後ろから刺された
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.63,default,,0,0,0,,You have just been\Nstabbed from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ それだけのことだ　散れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.29,default,,0,0,0,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.66,default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:03.18,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で あんな奴を…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.26,default,,0,0,0,,Why did I trust him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大事な勝負だと分かっていながら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.18,default,,0,0,0,,Despite knowing the\Nimportance of this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は なぜ自分で考えなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.02,default,,0,0,0,,why didn't I think for myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ自分で決めなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.85,default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I decide for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ他人に…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.11,default,,0,0,0,,Why did I let others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.65,default,,0,0,0,,...decide my fate\Non my behalf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の行く末を委ねちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:33.04,default,,0,0,0,,Regret was not enough\Nto describe his pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:35.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢悔い｣というには あまりに重い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:35.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身がちぎれるような悔い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.17,default,,0,0,0,,It's regret that\Nrips one's soul apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 考えてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.90,default,,0,0,0,,But thinking about it,\NKaiji realised that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういうことが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてではないことに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.38,default,,0,0,0,,...it wasn't the first time\Nhe went through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:42.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは気づく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろん これほどの痛手は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.17,default,,0,0,0,,Though the previous blows\Nwere not as bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:49.15,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Schools Attended]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までの人生の岐路で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもその判断を他人に委ね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.15,default,,0,0,0,,he'd left his life's\Nmajor decisions up to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流されて生きてきたことに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.17,default,,0,0,0,,and merely went with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その弱さが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この土壇場で出たことに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.50,default,,0,0,0,,That weakness showed\Nin such a place as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われない　こんなバカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:01.67,default,,0,0,0,,There's no help\Nfor a fool like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.29,default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason\Nfor me to be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.67,default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.\NJust do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,任せとけって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の言うとおりにすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら必勝法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.15,default,,0,0,0,,This is a\Nperfect winning technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.76,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.07,default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.18,default,,0,0,0,,Fool! There's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:17.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:17.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの あるわけねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.32,default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that\Nhe's deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だまそうとしてるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見え見えじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに このおっさんときたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.19,default,,0,0,0,,But looking at this old fogey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.64,default,,0,0,0,,It's his own fault for\Nnot thinking for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で決めない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの おっさんが悪いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船じゃ バカは朽ちるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.05,default,,0,0,0,,The idiots on this ship\Nare the first to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.20,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.01,default,,0,0,0,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年前 カイジを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金の保証人にした男
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:47.90,default,,0,0,0,,A year ago, he made Kaiji\Nstand guarantee for his loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:53.45,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata was the reason why\NKaiji was forced onto this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが この船に落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっかけとなった古畑だった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:57.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.35,default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちてやがったか 奴も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がすもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.09,default,,0,0,0,,Has he also\Nfallen into this pit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.09,default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑が消えたのは気分転換の部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.32,default,,0,0,0,,The room Furuhata went into\Nwas the break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場から逃れ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ちを落ち着かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.23,default,,0,0,0,,An oasis to escape\Nfrom the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかの間のオアシス
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.84,default,,0,0,0,,...and to calm oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし今 そこは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.84,default,,0,0,0,,But now, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹きだまり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.08,default,,0,0,0,,A mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗色濃厚の人間たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:28.52,default,,0,0,0,,People doomed to failure, holding\Ntheir heads in frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 一様に頭を抱えている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.63,default,,0,0,0,,A room of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嘆きの部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑も その１人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.55,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カード４枚 星１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.79,default,,0,0,0,,He had four cards\Nand one star left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.53,default,,0,0,0,,Even though Kaiji\Nwas better off,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:43.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジよりマシとはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:43.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼もまた絶望の渦中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.74,default,,0,0,0,,he was also in a\Nwhirlpool of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:47.73,default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Furuhata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.74,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:55.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す… すいません 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:55.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから出るんだ ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.20,default,,0,0,0,,- I...I'm sorry!\N- That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.24,default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな所にいたら腐っちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.62,default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in there,\Nyou'll rot away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も さっきまでそうだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偉そうなことは言えないが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.02,default,,0,0,0,,I was the same way\Na while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.59,default,,0,0,0,,so I can't talk big, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.10,default,,0,0,0,,Those guys aren't looking\Nfor possibilities at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴ら 可能性を見ていない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ちが状況に押しつぶされ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:24.10,default,,0,0,0,,They're shutting out what\Nlittle chance they have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:24.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかに残っている勝者への道を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:24.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら閉ざしている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも無理ないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次 負けたらと思うと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.61,default,,0,0,0,,But it's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.57,default,,0,0,0,,If you think of\Nlosing the next round...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:33.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:33.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力し合わねえか 俺たち？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:33.58,default,,0,0,0,,Hey Furuhata,\Nwhy don't we work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人で星を６つにするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.13,default,,0,0,0,,Let's get six stars\Nbetween the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人で？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 さっきいくら借りた？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.99,default,,0,0,0,,Both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.21,default,,0,0,0,,How much did you borrow just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,200です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.55,default,,0,0,0,,2 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は1000万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.19,default,,0,0,0,,I have 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.80,default,,0,0,0,,2 million isn't enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:50.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,200じゃ無理だが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:50.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万あれば星だって買える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.93,default,,0,0,0,,but 10 million would\Nbuy us enough stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:53.98,default,,0,0,0,,If we cooperate using your\Nremaining cards and my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の残してる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのカードと俺の金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人が協力すれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.80,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ　星だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:57.80,default,,0,0,0,,Stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.26,default,,0,0,0,,Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻ろう　さっきの部屋で探すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.91,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back\Nand search that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星２つでカード０の男をな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.19,default,,0,0,0,,For a guy with two stars\Nand no cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:16.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　あれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.73,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.38,default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるでカイジらと出会うために
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:21.89,default,,0,0,0,,As if Kaiji was fated to meet\Nthis man, there he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者かが用意したかのように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男は いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男の名は安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星２つにカード０
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.69,default,,0,0,0,,His name is Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.77,default,,0,0,0,,Two stars and no cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらとは また別の形で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望的な男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:33.50,default,,0,0,0,,A man in a different kind\Nof despair from Kaiji's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.71,default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:44.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから先は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:44.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人１人って考えは捨てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.08,default,,0,0,0,,Forget about thinking\Nabout yourself as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.95,default,,0,0,0,,Think of three as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:48.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人で１人　３人で１単位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.82,default,,0,0,0,,A unit of three persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人は運命共同体だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.05,default,,0,0,0,,Three persons,\Nlinked by one destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:55.11,default,,0,0,0,,Their total was 1.4 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人の金は計1400万
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星４つ　カード５枚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.83,default,,0,0,0,,They had four stars\Nand five cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの内訳は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ４枚にパー１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.56,default,,0,0,0,,The cards consisted of\Nfour Scissors and one Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪の状況だが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか３人で星を９個にするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:06.57,default,,0,0,0,,It's a worst possible scenario\Nbut let's get nine stars somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.07,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:12.24,default,,0,0,0,,And in this way, the weak\Nunited together to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱者たちは生き残りをかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動きだした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:16.08,default,,0,0,0,,The three moved forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へ 三者三様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれの足りない要素を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,補い合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.57,default,,0,0,0,,helping to compensate\Nfor each other's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢勝負｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.71,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Game.
